Searchify,is,a,hosted,search,engine,that,lets,users,add,full,text,search,to,their,application,without,configuring,and,hosting,their,own,search,infrastructure,Searchify,allows,users,to,tune,their,search,results,ranking,using,custom,scoring,functions,Searchify,also,acts,a,drop,in,replacement,for,existing,IndexTank,users,The,REST,API,defines,methods,to,manage,indexes,create,and,delete,operate,on,them,add,and,delete,documents,functions,etc,perform,searches,etc,It,uses,HTTP,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON